data.description: Privacy and Hunting abounds on 15+ acres.   Private lane that opens to a 3 bedroom 2 full bath rancher with total seclusion.  Master bedroom with master bath.  Open floor plan.  Sky lights.   Enjoy the fireplace from the dining room or sunken living room. Bring your vision to the large room off the kitchen with two separate entrances.  Walkout to the wrap around deck that overlooks approximately 1/2 acre fenced yard with a lean to shed.  The wood furnace in walkout basement offers a great way to save energy.  Also, enjoy the two car garage off the basement.  Some windows updated.  Both bathrooms updated. Septic new 2022.  Recent appraisal.    Property is zoned - NAR.  Zoning Use - Residential.  According to CC Planning and Zoning, there is full minor subdivision potential (4 lots + remaining lands) and potentially two new lots through major subdivision. Seller will make no claims.  Buyer is responsible for confirming with CC planning and zoning any subdivision potential, zoning, and land use.    Selling as is.  Must have an appointment.  Property is gated and security cameras are throughout.  Please do not drive to the property without an appointment.  Private lane is shared by others.  Owner occupied.
